RPX Insight Plans








Proprietary Insights








  
 Campaign Perspective 
View matters grouped by underlying patents and parties, with an assessment of plaintiff behavior, campaign events, and patent strength.






  
 Entity Profiles 
Download dossiers with hand-researched intelligence on entities, including their affiliations, litigation patterns, as well as patent acquisitions.






  
 News and Analysis 
Stay on top of recent trends, notable litigation events, and patent transactions through RPX Reports and the RPX Weekly Newsletter.










Core Knowledge








  
 Litigation Intelligence 
Access all patent suits filed in district court since 2000, as well as all PTAB petitions and ITC investigations, including analytics on campaigns, judges, and venues.






  
 Advanced Alerts 
Stay on top of developments related to your business or clients with the RPX Daily Litigation Alert as well as RPX Custom Alerts with precise fine-tuning options.






  
 Patent Information 
Research any US patent published since 1976 with statistics and visualizations on assignment and litigation histories.











